Bottle at Rex bar och grill in Ume. This is the first time I have sent a beer back because of the taste. Head and colour is fine, but I have never before tried a beer so full of diacetyl. I now understand the meaning of the word butter bomb. The reaction from the waitress is another story. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone
